    "is_daily_featured": true
  },
  {
    "title": "油价暴涨：你还在为“里程焦虑”买单吗？",
    "seo_summary": "全球油价波动，传统燃油车主每次加油都心惊肉跳。本文揭示电动车在成本和稳定性上的巨大优势，破除“里程焦虑”等常见误区，并探讨全球能源转型与国家安全、工业竞争的深层联系。",
    "url": "https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/maybe-you-should-have-bought-an-electric",
    "cover": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-renzhi-hub/main/assets/rss_covers/b61bd806db150594.jpeg",
    "wechat_html": "<section style='margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#fff;'><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzXgUR7FJnf11qGIo8nmKt6RxibXrb5s4RFb9UZ9UOHQy7fqQyI377Licw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'><section style='padding:0;'><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">你有没有在加油站，看着油价牌子悄悄叹气？</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">国际局势风云变幻，油价就像过山车，说涨就涨，你的通勤成本瞬间飙升。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">当你还在为那几十块钱的油费肉疼时，有人早已告别了加油站，夜夜安睡。</p><img peitu='true' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-renzhi-hub/main/assets/rss_covers/b61bd806db150594.jpeg' style='width:100%;display:block;margin:30px 0;'><section style=\"margin:50px 0 25px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5; padding-bottom:12px; display:flex; align-items:center;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block; width:5px; height:18px; background-color:#111; margin-right:12px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-size:19px; color:#111; letter-spacing:1.5px;\">油价飙升，谁在偷笑？</strong></section><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">面对油价飙升，你感到愤怒是理所当然。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">国际局势动荡，直接影响了你的日常出行。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">然而，有那么一群人，他们对油价的涨跌无动于衷。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">他们就是电动车车主。他们根本不去加油站。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">每天晚上把车停在车位，插上充电线，一觉醒来，车子就充满电了。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">相比燃油车，他们的出行成本低得多。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">有数据机构分析，每行驶一英里，电动车只需花费5美分。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">而传统燃油车则需要12美分。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">这还是油价上涨前的数字。</p><section style=\"margin:50px 0 25px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5; padding-bottom:12px; display:flex; align-items:center;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block; width:5px; height:18px; background-color:#111; margin-right:12px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-size:19px; color:#111; letter-spacing:1.5px;\">那些“电动车不行”的谎言</strong></section><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">多年来，你可能听过各种反对电动车的说法。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">有人说：“里程焦虑怎么办？”</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">但过去十年，电动车续航里程已经翻了三倍。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">有人说：“充电太慢了！”</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">他们不知道，电动车可以在你睡觉时充电。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">还有人担心：“电池矿物会不够用！”</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">但实际数据表明，这种担忧不成立。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">这些说法，无非是“恐惧、不确定和怀疑”（FUD）的混合体。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">它们阻碍了许多人接受新技术。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">结果是，全球电动车销量一路飙升。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">但在某些地区，销量却停滞不前，甚至下滑。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">比如美国，政策阻碍和市场误读，让它在全球竞争中掉队。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">中国、欧洲、新加坡和挪威等国家，电动车普及率远超美国。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">这意味着，下一代汽车产业的价值创造，很可能发生在别处。</p><section style=\"margin:50px 0 25px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5; padding-bottom:12px; display:flex; align-items:center;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block; width:5px; height:18px; background-color:#111; margin-right:12px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-size:19px; color:#111; letter-spacing:1.5px;\">油价为何总在“折磨”你？</strong></section><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">如果你开的是燃油车，你必须明白：油价波动是常态。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">原油价格极易受到供应冲击。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">短期内，石油需求弹性很小。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">即使供应略有中断，大部分人也无法停止开车上班。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">卡车、船舶、飞机也离不开石油。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">石油还是塑料等现代经济必需品的原料。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">所以一旦供应中断，比如霍尔木兹海峡（全球重要石油运输通道）受阻。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">油价就会迅速飙升。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">你只能被迫支付更高的价格。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">与此形成鲜明对比的是电力。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">电力价格波动远小于石油和汽油。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">如果你开电动车，你就不会受到这些周期性价格冲击的影响。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">现代无人机战争，让扼守关键海上通道变得更容易。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">全球任何地方的冲突，都可能导致油价暴涨。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">因此，能源转型不只是气候问题，更是国家安全问题。</p><section style=\"margin:50px 0 25px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5; padding-bottom:12px; display:flex; align-items:center;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block; width:5px; height:18px; background-color:#111; margin-right:12px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-size:19px; color:#111; letter-spacing:1.5px;\">全球行动：是时候做出你的选择</strong></section><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">面对能源危机，各国正在积极行动。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">菲律宾宣布进入国家能源紧急状态。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">斯里兰卡实施燃油配给。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">巴基斯坦关闭学校，削减政府车辆燃油配额。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">韩国、日本动用战略石油储备。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">许多国家不再只是依赖化石燃料。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">他们转而建设更多太阳能、风能和电池。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">油价上涨，也让全球消费者对电动车的热情空前高涨。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">在东南亚，比亚迪等中国电动车销量火爆。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">英国、丹麦的二手电动车搜索量飙升8万次。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">美国电动车在线搜索量也增长了20%。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">电池价格大幅下降，让电动车性能远超燃油车。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">那些固守燃油车技术的国家，将逐渐被全球市场边缘化。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">不拥抱技术创新，会付出沉重代价。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">当你在加油站为油价揪心时，那些明智的电动车主早已高枕无忧。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">告别油价波动，选择更稳定的未来。</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; line-height:2; color:#2c3e50; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-align:justify;\">这笔经济账，你该现在就算清。</p><section style='margin:45px 0 20px 0;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid #E5E5E5;'><section style='font-size:13px;color:#999;margin-bottom:12px;text-transform:uppercase;'>TAGS</section><section><span style='display:inline-block;margin:0 10px 10px 0;padding:4px 12px;border:1px solid #DCDFE6;color:#606266;font-size:12px;'>电动车</span><span style='display:inline-block;margin:0 10px 10px 0;padding:4px 12px;border:1px solid #DCDFE6;color:#606266;font-size:12px;'>油价</span><span style='display:inline-block;margin:0 10px 10px 0;padding:4px 12px;border:1px solid #DCDFE6;color:#606266;font-size:12px;'>能源转型</span><span style='display:inline-block;margin:0 10px 10px 0;padding:4px 12px;border:1px solid #DCDFE6;color:#606266;font-size:12px;'>汽车消费</span><span style='display:inline-block;margin:0 10px 10px 0;padding:4px 12px;border:1px solid #DCDFE6;color:#606266;font-size:12px;'>经济账</span></section></section></section><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzk57DCmhVC16o9ILH0Tn1YPEiarfLRRQSVFN2mJdeYibGnBPialPIzvojw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'></section>",
